hopobject.body: It's a bad line mymadisonpharmacy.com The 2013 Nobel Prize in physics will be announced on Tuesday and the chemistry award is set for Wednesday. The Swedish Academy will reveal its choice for the Nobel literature award on Thursday and a Norwegian committee will name the winner or winners of the Nobel Peace Prize on Friday. That award is always announced in Oslo, in line with the wishes of prize founder Alfred Nobel. This year's Nobel season ends with the economics award on Oct. 14.
